snippet.title: inFAMOUS™  2 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
inFAMOUS(tm) 2 continues the adventures of Cole MacGrath, the electrical superhero of Empire City. Now in search of new powers to save the world from the unstopable force called, The Beast, Cole will face new foes, make new allies, and ultimately decide the fate of the world.

Watch this exciting new trailer and get a glimpse of Cole's new journey!

inFAMOUS(tm) 2 is available now.
